#define GREETINGS ["Darlin', you look a lil' lost. This ain't a parade, it's a fight, and Remy don't want to ruin that pretty face.","Step aside, mon ami. I got a hot game of poker waiting on me, and you ain't even worth the price of admission.","You want to surrender now, or do you want to find out how much it hurts to get a pocket full of change blown up?","I've stolen from ancient gods and cosmic empires. You really think you're gonna clip the Ragin' Cajun?","Take a walk, cher. You look like you'd break if the wind blew too hard, let alone a full deck.","Nice weapon you got there. Mind if I borrow it? I promise I'll give it back... right before it goes boom.","You got a little spark in you, I give you that. But Gambit? He's a whole damn wildfire.","Let's keep this clean, yeah? I hate getting blood on the leather, it's a nightmare to get out.","You're playing a losing hand, friend. And Remy? He always knows how to read the bluff.","Come on then, show me what you got. Just try to keep up with the cards.","Now here's a face I recognize from the rogue's gallery. Let's see if your game matches your reputation, mon ami.","Place your bets, ladies and gentlemen. The Cajun's in the house, and the house always wins.","You look like a tough nut to crack. Good thing I brought a whole deck of explosives to help me out.","Don't blink, cher. You might miss the trick, and the trick is the part that hurts.","A fair match, a beautiful night... let's see if you can handle a little kinetic energy, yeah?","Alright, no more playing around. You hit hard enough to shake the bayou. Let's see how you handle the wildcard.","I can feel the energy coming off you from here. Let's see if my kinetic charge can short-circuit that attitude.","You're a big fish in a small pond, friend. But you just swam into a net made of pure explosions.","I've fought sentinels, aliens, and angry gods. You're just another Tuesday. Let's dance.","The stakes just went through the roof. I love a high-roller game.","You look like the kind of monster that doesn't know when to quit. Good thing I got an infinite deck.","I'm gonna need more than a few aces for this one... New Plan: Don't get hit, and blow up everything they touch.","You think that armor can protect you? Everything's got potential energy, friend. Even that big suit of yours.","The X-Men didn't send an army, they sent me. And trust me, I'm more than enough to make your night explode.","This might be the dumbest bet I've ever made... but Remy never folds on a full house!","You walk around like you own the stars, mon dieu. Let's see if a god can handle a kinetic chain reaction!","I've survived the Age of Apocalypse and the end of worlds. You don't scare me, entity. You just make me mad.","I don't care how big your power grid is. If it's made of matter, I can make it blow up!","This is for the whole damn planet, ain't it? Fine. Let's see if a cosmic god can face a true wildcard.","You're holding all the cards, ain't you? Well, Gambit's about to flip the damn table!","You can unmake reality, huh? Let's see if you can unmake the kinetic energy of an entire planet collapsing on your face!","I ain't a god, I'm just a thief from New Orleans... but today, I'm gonna steal your eternity!","The house has the deck stacked, the dealers are corrupt, and the game is rigged... but I'm still betting on a miracle!","If this is the end of the line, I'm going out with a bang that'll shake the multiverse. Watch the cards, deity!","(Blazing with uncontrolled, overloaded pink kinetic energy) YOU WANT A SHOW?! REMY'S ABOUT TO BLOW UP THE ENTIRE BOARD!!!"]

#define WrestleWin ["Like I said, darlin'—you was playing with a short deck. Better luck next time.","Remy didn't even have to take his hands out of his pockets for that one. Truly a shame.","I’ve seen toddlers fling mud with more kinetic force than that. Go on home, mon ami.","A full deck of cards, and I only needed the two of hearts to put you to sleep.","You fell for the oldest trick in the book. And Gambit wrote the chapter on misdirection.","You had a decent strategy, friend. Problem is, I don't play by the rules.","Boom. Just like that. The cards don't lie, and they said your time was up.","Nice try with the little weapon there. Too bad everything you touch belongs to Gambit.","You bet it all on a pair of deuces. A thief always knows when to call a bluff.","Don't look so sour. Getting beat by the Ragin' Cajun is practically an honor.","Never bet against a man who can turn a pocket full of loose change into a hand grenade.","That was a good run, mon ami. But when the stakes are real, the house always wins.","You kept up with the staff, you kept up with the kicks... but you forgot to watch the cards.","The name is Gambit, cher. Remember it next time you think about crossing the X-Men.","A beautiful night, a spectacular clash... and the wildcard takes the pot. Classic.","Whew! You almost had me cornered there. Had to pull a real rabbit out of the hat for that one.","You hit like a runaway train, friend. Good thing I'm a master at switching the tracks.","That kinetic chain reaction almost caught me too. We really blew the roof off this place, yeah?","You fought hard, and you fought clean. But a thief always finds the blind spot.","High-roller games always bring out the best in me. Thanks for the workout, power-player.","I told you... everything has potential energy. Even a giant, unstoppable monster like you!","My heart is beating like a drum... I really thought that final strike was gonna clip me. Full house beats a straight!","You broke my favorite bo staff, titan. But I guess turning it into a megaton bomb was worth it.","Never corner a thief. We get desperate, and a desperate Cajun makes a whole lot of things go boom.","The bigger they are, the harder they fall... and the bigger the explosion when they hit the dirt!","(Breathless chuckle) Mon dieu... I actually pulled it off. I just blew up a cosmic storm.","You held all the power of the stars, entity... but you let a mortal thief steal the match right from your hands.","I overloaded the kinetic energy of the very ground we stood on! You didn't just fight Remy... you fought the whole planet!","The X-Men taught me how to survive. Today, I survived a god. Let the record show the Cajun don't fold.","That was the highest-stakes bluff of my entire life... and I just cleared the whole damn table!","You unmade the deck... you unmade the rules... but you couldn't unmake the wildcard. Reality stays right here.","(Coughs, smiling through the pain) A thief from New Orleans just stole eternity from a god. Now that's a story.","I channeled the kinetic energy of a thousand collapsing realities right into your face. How's that for a magic trick?!","The odds were a billion to one against me. Good thing I never learned how to read the odds.","(Drops to one knee, looking at the sky) The house didn't win today, deity... Remy just broke the bank."]

#define WrestleDefeat ["Aw, come on now... a trick like that? That's just cheating, mon ami.","You slipped a cold deck on me... I didn't see that move coming at all. Remy hates losing a sucker bet.","Alright, alright, you got the drop on me. Just don't go telling the rest of the X-Men about this, yeah?","A total fluke. I tripped on my own trench coat, I swear it on the bayou!","You played a sloppy hand and somehow hit the jackpot. Enjoy it, cher, it won't happen twice.","Ugh... my staff is cracked, my cards are scattered. You played a good game, friend.","The cards just weren't falling my way tonight. The Cajun folds.","A clean hit. I didn't think you had the speed to clip me, but I stand corrected.","Looks like you held the ace up your sleeve after all. Take the pot and go.","My kinetic charge didn't detonate in time... a bad gamble on my part.","Whew... you really know how to disrupt a man's flow. My head is spinnin' like a roulette wheel.","You called my bluff and you had the cards to back it up. Fair play, mon ami.","I dodged left when I should've jumped right. That's the game, I suppose.","The Ragin' Cajun is officially out of cards. Mind if I take a rain check on the rest of this fight?","You broke my rhythm, cher. A beautiful performance... even if it leaves me in the dirt.","That strike... felt like a freight train hitting a bicycle. Remy's out of commission...","I threw a whole straight flush of charged cards at you... and you just walked right through 'em...","My kinetic energy couldn't breach your defenses. Guess the house really does win sometimes.","I'm bleeding all over my favorite leather coat... You're a tough customer, power-player.","X-Men... fall back... this one's got the deck stacked entirely too high...","I couldn't dodge... you're too fast for something that big... mon dieu...","I tried to overload your armor... but the feedback... it nearly tore my own arms off...","No more quips... no more cards... I got nothing left to bet with...","You're a walking natural disaster. Remy's luck... finally ran completely dry.","Can't stand up... my legs are like lead. Go on, titan... finish the game...","I tried to bluff a god... what a stupid, arrogant thief I am... (Coughs)","You didn't just beat me... you unmade the kinetic energy in my body... I can't even move my fingers...","I fought for my world... but you hold the stars in your hand. Rogue... I'm sorry, cher...","My cards are just ash in the wind before you. A cosmic storm always beats a wildcard.","I put everything into that last explosion... and it didn't even scratch your paint. Incredible...","You unmade reality... you tore up the board... but it was a hell of a run, wasn't it?...","A thief from New Orleans... standing against the end of space and time... At least I went out in style...","(Faint, breathless whisper) The game was rigged from the start... but I'd play it... all over again...","My atoms are scattering into the void... the pink light is fading... Game over...","You won the multiverse... deity... but you'll never forget... the name... Gambit..."]
